a sampler for the conll format, it accepts an input file, output destination file and a number (or percent),
samples according to input and writes the sampled data to the output file

usage: 
conllSampler.py trainData.conll sampledDataFileName.conll 80
conllSampler.py trainData.conll sampledDataFileName.conll 15%
conllSampler.py trainData.conll sampledDataFileName.conll 0.1%
